name: Fluffyrock e17 YS-mod
description:
This model is a merge of Lodestones "Fluffyrock" model (fluffyrock-576-704-832-960-1088-lion-low-lr-e17) with a 3.6% addition of a merge of Yiffye18 and AnyEasterSnack V1. It is geared towards broadening the styles and Results possible in the very good Fluffyrock model without losing too much of said quality.

I am not Lodestone and would advice all to check his original work at https://huggingface.co/lodestones or on the Furry Diffusion Discord https://discord.com/invite/JKS7UttReS

As its mostly their model, with only a minor tweak, i would give all credit to him, with derpyness being caused by my modification.
